title: [Gyldemar Forest, Standing Stone]
description: A number of the stone ramps have been placed here, their blunt ends now joined.  The ramp pairs encircle a larger ramp with an enormous block of stone at one end.

A number of the stone ramps have been placed here, their blunt ends pressed together.  The ramp pairs encircle a larger ramp with an enormous block of stone at one end.  The dark grey color of the stones seem almost black in the starlight.
